    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are having a trouble on udemy course of chad on springboot for the importing the jar. Then follow these steps.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Right click on the project.</li>\n<li>You will see a option of Build Path, click on it.</li>\n<li>You will have a option of Configure Build path, click on it.</li>\n<li>Go to libraries.</li>\n<li>Then go to the place where you have a jar files make them into a new folder and upload on a new place.</li>\n<li>Then click on Add External Jars, you will surely be able to upload it which will help on classpathxmlapplicationcontext as well.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Thank you.</p>\n"
